article_title: U.S. figure skater Ashley Wagner is not pleased with her score
article_text:
Topics: 2014 Olympics, ashley wagner, Figure skating, memes, sochi, Entertainment News

Ashley Wagner may have just become the McKayla Maroney of the Winter Games. Though the 22-year-old seemed pleased with her performance in the women’s short program of the figure skating team event, the judges were not as impressed. The Olympic figure skater scored a 63.10, placing fourth, behind Japan’s Mao Asada — who fell during her routine. This was Wagner’s reaction to the score:

The moment has emerged in gif form, so the Internet can remember Wagner’s disappointment forever and ever.

(Gif via Deadspin.com)
